OL,3,CCouncils weigh plans to convert
OL,4,Chousing for asylum seekers
OL,6,FCouncils across the South are weighing
OL,7,Fup plans to convert housing for asylum
OL,8,Fseekers as part of a Government push
OL,9,Fto slash the cost of migrant
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FThe Government is making funds
OL,13,Favailable for local authorities to
OL,14,Fprovide basic housing for asylum
OL,15,Fseekers in a bid to cut down on its
OL,16,Fhuge expenditure on hotels.
OL,18,FITV Meridian asked 24 councils across
OL,19,Fthe South East whether they had
OL,20,Fregistered interest in the Home Office
OL,21,FAsylum Fund.
