OL,3,CCouncils weigh plans to convert
OL,4,Chousing for asylum seekers
OL,6,FBrighton and Hove City Council and
OL,7,FCanterbury City Council have confirmed
OL,8,Fthey have registered their interest in
OL,9,Fthe pilot project.
OL,11,FMedway Council and Folkestone District
OL,12,FCouncil also registered their interest
OL,13,Fbut were not selected by the
OL,14,FGovernment.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Thanet District Council
OL,17,Fsaid it is still considering its
OL,18,Foptions. The remaining councils said
OL,19,Fthey have either not applied for the
OL,20,Fscheme or are not eligible for the
OL,21,Ffunding.
