OL,3,CCouncils weigh plans to convert
OL,4,Chousing for asylum seekers
OL,6,FThe Government funding available has
OL,7,Fnot been confirmed. However, one
OL,8,Fcouncillor claimed the total could
OL,9,Freach up to #500 million.
OL,11,FAuthorities which successfully bid for
OL,12,Ffunds will either buy housing or bring
OL,13,Fderelict properties back into use for
OL,14,Ftemporary occupation by asylum seekers.
OL,16,FITV Meridian understands that after
OL,17,Ften years, the homes would become part
OL,18,Fof councils' stock of social housing.
