OL,3,CCouncils weigh plans to convert
OL,4,Chousing for asylum seekers
OL,6,FBella Sankey, Labour councillor and
OL,7,Fleader of Brighton and Hove Council,
OL,8,Fsaid the funding would help local
OL,9,Fauthorities invest in housing and
OL,10,Frevive disused sites.
OL,12,F"From my perspective it's incredibly
OL,13,Fimportant that local authorities are
OL,14,Fempowered to invest in their housing
OL,15,Fstock," she said.
OL,17,F"That will ultimately be a good thing
OL,18,Ffor local resident populations who are
OL,19,Fin need of housing and for people
OL,20,Fseeking asylum as well."
