OL,3,CCouncils weigh plans to convert
OL,4,Chousing for asylum seekers
OL,6,FNot all councillors are convinced,
OL,7,Fhowever. Alistair McNair, Conservative
OL,8,Fcouncillor for Brighton and Hove
OL,9,FCouncil, said it risked encouraging
OL,10,Fillegal immigration.
OL,12,F"This is another way of attracting
OL,13,Fmore illegal immigrants to the
OL,14,Fcountry, if they know they're going to
OL,15,Fbe put up in nice accommodation," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "We need to have policies in
OL,17,Fplace to stop illegal immigrants
OL,18,Fcoming here."
