OL,3,CCouncils weigh plans to convert
OL,4,Chousing for asylum seekers
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Asylum seekers are not eligible for
OL,8,Fsocial housing.
OL,10,F"This government will close every
OL,11,Fasylum hotel. Work is well underway,
OL,12,Fwith more suitable sites being brought
OL,13,Fforward to ease pressure on
OL,14,Fcommunities and cut asylum costs.
OL,16,FThey added: "We are working closely
OL,17,Fwith local authorities, property
OL,18,Fpartners and across-government so that
OL,19,Fwe can accelerate delivery."
